
# CareerNext

CareerNext is a Laravel-based job portal platform designed to help users explore careers, apply for jobs, and manage their profiles through an intuitive admin and user interface.

## 🚀 Features

- Admin Dashboard with Authentication
- Job Posting and Application System
- User Registration & Login
- Fully Responsive Design
- Database Seeding for Demo Data

## 🛠️ Technologies Used

- Laravel 10+
- PHP 8.1+
- MySQL
- Composer
- Bootstrap
- JavaScript

## 📦 Installation

For complete installation steps, please refer to the [INSTALL.md](INSTALL.md) file.

